.DS_Store
node_modules/
*.log
server/db/notdnd.sqlite
server/db/notdnd.sqlite-shm
server/db/notdnd.sqlite-wal
server/db/notdnd.db.json
server/db/notdnd.db.json.bak
backups/
.env

# Generated NPC portrait / image assets (never commit binaries)
data/assets/

# Runtime logs (request log, run logs, gm-capture, transcripts) — all churn, never commit.
data/logs/

# Runtime play/test campaigns (cmp_* runs written at play time). The seed cmp_001 and
# any already-committed campaigns stay tracked; this only stops NEW runtime runs from
# dirtying the tree — same treatment as data/assets/ and the SQLite DB.
data/campaigns/

# Runtime waitlist store (server-written signups; the SQLite `waitlist` table is the
# durable copy). Was tracked and accreting smoke-test debris — now ignored like the DB.
server/db/waitlist.json

# Local DB backups (e.g. *.pre-hygiene.bak from a coordinated migration) — safety nets,
# never versioned.
server/db/*.bak

# Owner's ComfyUI workflow exports (machine-specific API graphs w/ a local checkpoint
# path; loaded by generate.mjs at runtime, never committed). The committed per-style
# recipes (anime.json, dark-fantasy.json, realistic.json) are NOT matched by this.
scripts/art/workflows/*-realistic.json

# Beta-thumb owner-feedback dataset (runtime, per-box; never commit)
data/owner-verdicts.jsonl
